  • Method Details

    • createBaseProduct

      void createBaseProduct(String title, double rating, int calories, int protein, int fat, int sodium, int price)
      Creates a new base product by adding it to the menu, having the given attributes.
      Parameters:
      title - is the name of the product
      rating - is the rating oh the product
      calories - is the number of calories
      protein - is the protein amount for the product
      fat - is the fat amount
      sodium - is the sodium amount
      price - is the price of the product
      pre
      there is a logged-in user, the type of user is admin, there isn't already a product with that name
      post
      a new product with the specified attributes is present, the number of products is increased by 1
      invariant
      isWellFormed

    • logIn

      boolean logIn(String userName, String password)
      If the provided userName matches the password, the user can log-in.
      Parameters:
      userName - is the username of the user who wants to log in
      password - is the provided password
      Returns:
      true if userName and password match
      pre
      there is no other logged-in user
      post
      loggedInUser will become the user with userName and given password
      invariant
      isWellFormed()

    • logOut

      void logOut()
      The currently loggedInUser logs out
      pre
      there is a logged-in user
      post
      there is no logged-in user anymore
      invariant
      isWellFormed()

    • registerUser

      User registerUser(String userName, String password, TypeOfUser type)
      Registers a new user to the food delivery system
      Parameters:
      userName - is the username of the new user
      password - is the password of the new user
      type - is the type of the user (client, employee, admin)
      Returns:
      the user
      pre
      there is no user with the provided username and password
      post
      a user with the provided username and password will exist, the number of users increases by 1
      invariant
      isWellFormed()
